27#ifndef _ZMOD_H
28#define _ZMOD_H
29
30#pragma ident "%Z%%M% %I% %E% SMI"
31
32#ifdef __cplusplus
33extern "C" {
34#endif
35
36/*
37 * zmod - RFC-1950-compatible decompression routines
38 *
39 * This file provides the public interfaces to zmod, an in-kernel RFC 1950
40 * decompression library. More information about the implementation of these
41 * interfaces can be found in the usr/src/uts/common/zmod/ directory.
42 */
43
44#define Z_OK 0
45#define Z_STREAM_END 1
46#define Z_NEED_DICT 2
47#define Z_ERRNO (-1)
48#define Z_STREAM_ERROR (-2)
49#define Z_DATA_ERROR (-3)
50#define Z_MEM_ERROR (-4)
51#define Z_BUF_ERROR (-5)
52#define Z_VERSION_ERROR (-6)
53
54#define Z_NO_COMPRESSION 0
55#define Z_BEST_SPEED 1
56#define Z_BEST_COMPRESSION 9
57#define Z_DEFAULT_COMPRESSION (-1)
58
59extern int z_uncompress(void *, size_t *, const void *, size_t);
60extern int z_compress(void *, size_t *, const void *, size_t);
61extern int z_compress_level(void *, size_t *, const void *, size_t, int);
62extern const char *z_strerror(int);
63
64#ifdef __cplusplus
65}
66#endif
67
68#endif /* _ZMOD_H */
